{"tid":1349122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗遊行入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:04:02.000Z","uid":206546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07857fe26a51f4f1a9c51544207e323fbf11ac49","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"第一次開post可能有啲亂<br />\n我想講，元朗遊行應該以<span style=\"color: red;\">保護市民安全</span>返屋企不受襲擊為目標，我地應該要保護市民等佢地唔會再比牛屎佬打，我地唔應該好似啲黑社會咁，我地自己人比人打我地就打返佢地，我地要避免有任何嘅市民，再比呢班牛屎佬傷害，所以我地去元朗既目標應該係<span style=\"color: red;\">保護市民安全</span>。<br />\n更何況我地呢一場運動，要針對嘅係個政府，千祈唔好將佢變成我地同牛屎佬之間嘅打鬥<br />\n如果講錯啲咩唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"672e781e44d7bbf163c4e347e5520cf7104b88e0","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"543f8cd3c96cd16da2e17871a1dee093e56d0725","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:41:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 </span>"},{"pid":"c55ae6f06ee70839c3de116fc49bb5f42b7bcb6e","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5adec0e718d0268bcb93ac2a3982fb6083913388","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"上環好大獲啊！好多人都唔知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cfae0af2ae1ac3fd2279bd07cd1cb33306789a88","tid":1349122,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"另外希望大家都要關注下上環發生咩事"},{"pi